node.text:
A good friend of mine @marquelrussell said that what keeps most people from making $100k per month is the fact that they currently make $50k per month.

Im actually sitting with @derrickgracetwo who exemplifies and understands this. Why not just leave the boat there, do you really need to burn it?

I admire a man who chooses his vision over current success, no matter how much success you’re having, the vision is always greater.

@derrickgracetwo gave a very strong interview on the @socialproofpodcast this is the one you gotta check out! 

SHARE WITH A FRIEND!!
